{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game in the genre of single-player 2D Horror with adventure elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single player game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creepy atmosphere</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This story tells about the tragedy of three friends. Longtime friends Nick and Steve, as well as their friend Veta, were hospitalized due to accidents. This pair of friends, although severely injured, only ended up in purgatory. Each of them will have their own test, but their enemy will be common to all. &quot;She&quot; will not stop until they understand that in life you need to look only for the good, and not cry over trifles, that life needs to be appreciated, and not to mock it and be selfish, not appreciating what you have. Help them go through all the &quot;Hellish&quot; adventures so that they can realize their mistakes and defeat &quot;her&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The basis of the gameplay is simple: travel through locations, collecting everything you need to advance! Be vigilant, because every reaper has its own mechanics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Good luck, player, because I will come for each of you&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Note: although the game contains small elements of &quot;Backrooms&quot; (for example, moving through levels, or canonical level zero), <strong><u>it has nothing to do with the ent of this universe!!!</u></strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Missing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3080170/e5a325ef7471d20082e77ceb4579683a92df4d10.jpg"},{"name":"Twin brother","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3080170/ffad09a40cd24f2f8cd090c19a84675bafe37dd